            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#频繁挖耳朵易引发耳道疾病#】医生介绍，耳屎，学名“耵聍”，是外耳道分泌的一种淡黄色黏稠液体。#耳屎其实能保护耳道和鼓膜#，一般在说话、打哈欠时会...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E9%A2%91%E7%B9%81%E6%8C%96%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%B5%E6%98%93%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E8%80%B3%E9%81%93%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%23&amp;extparam=%23%E9%A2%91%E7%B9%81%E6%8C%96%E8%80%B3%E6%9C%B5%E6%98%93%E5%BC%95%E5%8F%91%E8%80%B3%E9%81%93%E7%96%BE%E7%97%85%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#频繁挖耳朵易引发耳道疾病#</span></a>】医生介绍，耳屎，学名“耵聍”，是外耳道分泌的一种淡黄色黏稠液体。<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E8%80%B3%E5%B1%8E%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%9E%E8%83%BD%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E8%80%B3%E9%81%93%E5%92%8C%E9%BC%93%E8%86%9C%23&amp;extparam=%23%E8%80%B3%E5%B1%8E%E5%85%B6%E5%AE%9E%E8%83%BD%E4%BF%9D%E6%8A%A4%E8%80%B3%E9%81%93%E5%92%8C%E9%BC%93%E8%86%9C%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#耳屎其实能保护耳道和鼓膜#</span></a>，一般在说话、打哈欠时会随下颌运动缓慢自动排出。常挖耳朵，尤其是用硬物挖，易诱发炎症、损伤鼓膜。平时感觉耳朵不舒服，可用干净棉签轻蹭，耵聍即可脱落。 <a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:4891081792487520" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax4.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hd1a62ly6fj60ry0fq7er02.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/1jynxhkclx084HMJAW6I01041201nCQ40E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1681651712&amp;ssig=CtbNEl8eee&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/ISRnM2zXlx084HMJfW6Q01041200Jaeb0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1681651712&amp;ssig=32wckefwA1&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/27KRMCnnlx084HMItl0Y01041200sLIG0E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1681651712&amp;ssig=8dXCAD315d&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A4891081792487520&amp;luicode=10000011&amp;lfid=1076032831150640" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
